<seg id="77">Under the rules of the Czech Republic, contracting authorities are free to choose between open and non-open procedures.</seg>
<seg id="78">In Germany, on the other hand, the legal and budgetary primacy of the open procedure for EU-wide contracts or the public tender, which corresponds to the open procedure for national contracts, applies.</seg>
