<seg id="225">Performance descriptions with performance units</seg>
<seg id="226">In the case of construction projects in some industrial areas, the contracting authority did not clearly specify the scope and type of services required in the service descriptions.</seg>
<seg id="227">As performance units, it only specified the converted space of the individual buildings in cubic meters.</seg>
<seg id="228">Completeness of service descriptions</seg>
<seg id="229">During the construction of a motorway bypass, the service descriptions were changed four times in the period August to September 2009 as part of a non-open procedure,</seg>
