<seg id="795">Summary findings</seg>
<seg id="796">The regulations on documentation and reporting and reporting requirements are largely identical in both countries and implement the EU requirements.</seg>
<seg id="797">The transparency of procurement procedures, including the awarding of contracts, is thus guaranteed in principle.</seg>
<seg id="798">The regulations to be applied in the Czech Republic go a little further than the requirements in Germany.</seg>
<seg id="799">The shortcomings identified in the documentation and in the announcements significantly limited the anti-corruption effect of these instruments in the respective procurement procedures.</seg>
