<p>
<seg id="1">VAT administration in the Czech Republic and the Federal Republic of Germany</seg>
<seg id="2">Report on the audit</seg>
<seg id="3">Preface</seg>
<seg id="4">Taxes are the most important source of income for public budgets.</seg>
<seg id="5">The audit of this area should therefore be a focus of the work of the courts of auditors.</seg>
<seg id="6">This is especially true for VAT fraud.</seg>
