<seg id="78">4. Mutual assistance in the recovery of claims</seg>
<seg id="79">Intergovernmental mutual assistance in debt recovery is subject to the same European legislation in all Member States.</seg>
<seg id="80">Therefore, requests for intergovernmental administrative assistance in the recovery of claims in the CZ and Germany are processed in the same way.</seg>
