<seg id="111">3.3 Cooperation between the two auditors</seg>
<seg id="112">Prior to the parallel audit, the representatives of both audit institutions met in September 2008 to discuss and define the audit topics.</seg>
<seg id="113">In December 2008, the presidents of both audit institutions signed the agreement on cooperation in parallel auditing.</seg>
<seg id="114">At a meeting in Bonn in June 2009, the examination teams informed themselves about the first results obtained during exam preparation, discussed possible examination approaches and agreed on the further procedure.</seg>
