<seg id="119">4. Audit of VAT administration in selected areas</seg>
<seg id="120">4.1 Implementation of the recommendations from the first joint examination</seg>
<seg id="121">4.1.1 Implementation of recommendations in the Czech Republic</seg>
<seg id="122">Recommendation 1</seg>
<seg id="123">Harmonisation of requirements for registration of taxpayers within the EU Supported</seg>
<seg id="124">Based on the results of the first audit, the Czech Court of Auditors recommended to adapt the requirements for VAT registration and to introduce new rules for the cancellation of registration in the CZ.</seg>
<seg id="125">These revised rules should more effectively reduce the risk of possible tax evasion.</seg>
